Center of the Courtyard~
This is the center of the large courtyard, which is by far the most
beautiful part of the city of Caergoth.  At each end of this rather large
courtyard, for major roads converge.  Subsequently, this road is one of the
busiest in the town.  Nearly everybody passing through the city has to come
through here, which leads to a multitude of different types of people. 
Also, at the center stands a fountain, shooting gleaming water skyward, with
citizens and explorers gathered around it.  
