Michael's Shop of Wizardry~
In this medium sized shop, much clutter is about.  Among the things that
stand out from the mess are two bookcases, made of a dark wood.  They are
towering over the rest of the shop.  Books of all types, some dating far
back, some from fairly modern times are lining these shelves.  Near these
shelves are robed figures, most huddling over a book.  Also, at the back of
the shop is a man in the red cloaks of Lunitari.  Surrounding him are
floating discs, with various potions, scrolls, and staffs among them. 
There's a little indentation on one of the discs noting it as Michael's.  
